& [PrecheckResult] is no_exact_theorem_target_yet
  + [found_existing_target] is no
  + [reason] is local records contain an operator frame and a harmonic-pressure target frame, but no component-level map from the source tail budget to same-cylinder pressure smallness
  + [best_next_target] is local_suitable_pressure_frame_mapping
  + [specific_question] is whether the source tail components map to harmonic pressure p_h, local pressure p_0, projected-pressure remainder, or outside cutoff/nonlocal debris
  + [Deep_Research_Priority_Gate] is not_triggered
