& [DevelopedUnderstanding] is the current shape of meaning
  + [old_shape] is prospect for a theorem converting source tail budget directly to pressure smallness
  + [new_shape] is the direct theorem is not locally present; the responsible next step is to map tail components into the local suitable pressure decomposition before searching farther
  + [meaning_gained] is the bridge obstruction has moved from generic pressure smallness to a slot-assignment problem inside the accepted local pressure frame
  + [proof_promotion_status] is blocked
  + [lock_mass_change] is none

& [NextBoundedMotion] is follow-up
